Package circeIsland.elements

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Element
    This class represents an Element, which makes up each grid of the island.
    GardenLand
    This class represents Garden Land, which is a type of land that Circe can plant plants on.
    Holdable
    This class represents all of the items that are able to be held by Circe and added to storage.
    House
    This class represents the House Element, which are either Nymph Houses or Circe Houses.
    Land
    This class represents land, which makes up the bulk of the island
    PigPen
    This class represents a Pig Pen, where pigs live
    Pond
    This class represents a Pond, from which Circe can get water
